page.title: 12MY TYPICAL SATURDAY
page.content: On{Saturdays}I get washed and dressed, I get my{breakfast}and watch {T.V.}I then call for my friend. My brother comes out and we go to Harrogate field where we play{speedway Then we go to the shops for the dog and cat food and sometimes the vegtables. Sometimes we go to {Stockport}and go in the shops, and sometimes we buy things. When we get home we have our tea. Sometimes we go to{speedway (Belle {Vue).}We go on the bus to{Belle Vue and it costs Â£1.50 (inciuding programme). On the way home, we tell my friends dad about it. At home I go in with my brother,it is now about 11 'o' clock so at about 11.30, I get a drink and go to bed.
